title: Rancho Relaxo To Go
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Fast food, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Mexican, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Prior to Aug 2015 it operated a restaurant & bar at 300 College St (now shut). Moved and re-opened here Dec 2015 as primarily to-go / fast food concept. Menu has a fried cauliflower taco with avocado crema and pico de gallo, a portobello or veggie quesadilla, and a build-your-own burrito option. Has seating.
